VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \beval\s*\(|new\s+Function\s*\(|vm\.runIn
WHEN EXPR MISSING:trusted|allowlist && MISSING:test|spec|mock|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects dynamic code execution sinks in application flows.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Nestjs Injection Sink (Eval/Function).
